                <para styleclass="Body Text"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Edit-Active-Motion-Settings" anchor="MotionAccessibility" styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">MotionDesigner &gt; Edit toolbar &gt; Active Motion Settings</link><text styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true"> &gt; Accessibility tab &gt; Overlay Trace</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> color button.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
