    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><anchor id="OverlayTracePrepare" styleclass="VariableName"><keywords><keyword translate="true">Overlay Trace<keyword translate="true">Prepare the Data</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_" translate="true">Prepare the Data for an Overlay Trace</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">The data in the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Data-Transfer Table should be arranged as follows:</text></para>
          <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Data</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> in </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Column 2, from Row 0, will display in the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Position</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> graph.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Data</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> in </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Column 3, from Row 0, will display in the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Velocity</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> graph.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Data</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> in </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Column 4, from Row 0, will display in the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Acceleration</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> graph.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Data</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> in </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Column 5, from Row 0, will display in the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Jerk</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> graph.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Note</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">: Even if the data in each column are not motion-derivatives of each other, the data is displayed.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_" translate="true">Overlay-Trace example:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">To show the motion-values of </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion0</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> as an </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Overlay Trace</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> in </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion1.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">If necessary:</text></para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">Click </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-File-AddMotion" styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">File toolbar &gt; Add Motion</link><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true"> to add a </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion1</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true"> as a new motion name-tab</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">Click </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-View-Toolbar" styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">View toolbar</link><text styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true"> &gt; P, V, A, J</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true"> buttons to show all motion-derivatives in </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion1</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion0 name-tab</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true"> to make it the active motion</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">View toolbar &gt; P, V, A, J</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true"> buttons to show all motion-derivatives in </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion0</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Open the Data-Transfer Table.</text></para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="T_Menu" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="T_Menu"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">Click </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Tools-DataTransferTable" styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">Blend-Point and Segment Editor toolbar &gt; Data-Transfer Table</link><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">We want to get the motion-values from Motion0 into the Data-Transfer Table.</text></para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">Click </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Tools-DataTransfer-GetMotionData" styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">Data-Transfer Table &gt; Get Motion Data</link><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Data-Transfer Table</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> will fill with the motion-values for each motion-derivative in </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion0.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Make Motion1 the active motion.</text></para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion1 name-tab</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true"> to make it the active motion</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Show the data that is in the Data-Transfer Table as the Overlay-Trace in Motion1.</text></para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">Data-Transfer Table &gt; Overlay Trace</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">button</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">You will see the motion-values of </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion0</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> as an </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Overlay Trace</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> in </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion1</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Click in the Graph of Motion1 to re-scale </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion1</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> and the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Overlay Trace</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">The graphs should rescale to show the maximum and minimum of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion1</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> and the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Overlay-Trace.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
